如何使用第三方模块：
1安装完之后在要使用的地方：
import sys 
sys.path.append('your module path')
import module|||import function|class|something from your module

#then  you   can  use  it  !!!   try  it 
 
2.the second way :
you can add the module path to the system  environment variable

you can do the step:
1)creat a new system environment variable named PYTHONPATH
2)to add the path of you lib and module to it (if you don't the format of it,just look at the environment variable of PATH^_^)

